(44, 7, 49, 19, 11, 4, 4, NULL, 'Divine Presence in Heaven', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of God''s throne in heaven, highlighting His sovereignty and presence. Acts 7:49 questions the adequacy of a physical house for God, while Psalms 11:4 affirms His throne''s location in heaven.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
